A farmhouse occupied by the makrofests was evicted
The invaders had taken over 11 of the 13 floors of the building, in Balmes, 51
The 12 occupants left the estate yesterday at noon without offering any resistance.
Everything seems to indicate that the nightmare that the residents of 51 rue de Balmes lived in has come to an end.
Twelve people left the building yesterday at noon voluntarily, where they were organizing a neighborhood-wide mass mass, by court order and without the need for police intervention.
When the operation was over, the door lock was changed to prevent a repeat of the situation.
